{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-84-monopoly-odds","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","demoType":null,"title":"Zoezi la 84: uwezekano wa monopoly","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U igri <em>Monopoly</em>, standardna tabla je raspoređena na sledeći način:</p>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n  <table cellspacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"5\" border=\"0\" style=\"background-color: black; color: black;\" align=\"center\">\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">GO</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">A1</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">CC1</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">A2</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">T1</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">R1</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">B1</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">CH1</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">B2</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">B3</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">JAIL</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">H2</td>\n        <td colspan=\"9\">&nbsp;</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">C1</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">T2</td>\n        <td colspan=\"9\">&nbsp;</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">U1</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">H1</td>\n        <td colspan=\"9\">&nbsp;</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">C2</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">CH3</td>\n        <td colspan=\"9\">&nbsp;</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">C3</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">R4</td>\n        <td colspan=\"9\">&nbsp;</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">R2</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">G3</td>\n        <td colspan=\"9\">&nbsp;</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">D1</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">CC3</td>\n        <td colspan=\"9\">&nbsp;</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">CC2</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">G2</td>\n        <td colspan=\"9\">&nbsp;</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">D2</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">G1</td>\n        <td colspan=\"9\">&nbsp;</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">D3</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">G2J</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">F3</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">U2</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">F2</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">F1</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">R3</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">E3</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">E2</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">CH2</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">E1</td>\n        <td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: black; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;\">FP</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div><br>\n<p>Igrač počinje na polju GO i sabira rezultate dva šestostranačna bacanja kockica kako bi odredio koliko polja se pomera u smeru kazaljke na satu. Bez ikakvih dodatnih pravila, očekivali bismo da svako polje bude posećeno sa istom verovatnoćom: 2,5%. Međutim, dolazak na G2J (Idi u zatvor), CC (Community Chest) i CH (Chance) menja ovu raspodelu.</p>\n<p>Pored G2J, kao i po jedne karte iz špilova CC i CH koje nalažu igraču da odmah ode u zatvor, ako igrač baci tri uzastopna dupla, ne pomera se prema rezultatu trećeg bacanja, već odmah odlazi u zatvor.</p>\n<p>Na početku igre špilovi CC i CH se promešaju. Kada igrač stane na CC ili CH, uzima kartu sa vrha odgovarajućeg špila i, nakon izvršavanja uputstva, karta se vraća na dno špila. Svaki špil sadrži šesnaest karata, ali za potrebe ovog izazova razmatraju se samo karte koje utiču na kretanje; sva ostala uputstva se ignorišu i igrač ostaje na polju CC ili CH.</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Zajednica sanduk (kartica 2/16):</li>\n  <ol>\n    <li>Krećite do GO</li>\n    <li>Idite u zatvor</li>\n  </ol>\n  <li>Chance (kadi 10/16):</li>\n  <ol>\n    <li>Sogea hadi GO</li>\n    <li>Nenda gerezani</li>\n    <li>Nenda C1</li>\n    <li>Nenda E3</li>\n    <li>Nenda H2</li>\n    <li>Nenda R1</li>\n    <li>Nenda R inayofuata (kampuni ya reli)</li>\n    <li>Nenda R inayofuata</li>\n    <li>Nenda U inayofuata (kampuni ya huduma)</li>\n    <li>Rudi nyuma mraba 3.</li>\n  </ol>\n</ul>\n<p>Osnov za ovaj izazov je verovatnoća posećivanja određenog kvadrata. To jest, verovatnoća završavanja na tom kvadratu nakon skoka. Jer mora biti jasno da, osim G2J gde je verovatnoća završetka nula, CH kvadrati će imati najnižu verovatnoću, jer 5/8 moraju pomeriti do drugog kvadrata, a onaj koji nas zanima je poslednji kvadrat na kojem igrač završi svaki skok. Nećemo razlikovati između \"samo posete\" i slanja u zatvor, niti ćemo uzimati u obzir pravilo da treba dva puta da bi se \"izlazak iz zatvora\", pretpostavljajući da plaćaju kako bi izašli na sledeći potez.</p>\n<p>Počevši od polja GO i numerišući polja redom od 00 do 39, možemo spojiti ove dvocifrene brojeve kako bismo formirali nisku koja predstavlja skup polja.</p>\n<p>Analiza pokazuje da su najposećenija polja, redom, JAIL (6,24%) = polje 10, E3 (3,18%) = polje 24 i GO (3,09%) = polje 00. Zato se ova tri najposećenija polja mogu predstaviti šestocifrenim nizom <code>102400</code>.</p>\n<p>Ako se, umesto dve šestostrane kockice, koriste dve kockice sa po <code>n</code> strana, pronađi šestocifreni niz koji predstavlja najverovatniji raspored polja.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f3c11000cf542c50fed3","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302198,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-84-monopoly-odds"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function monopolyOdds(n) {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nmonopolyOdds(8);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>monopolyOdds(8)</code> trebalo bi da vrati niz slova.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof monopolyOdds(8) === 'string');"},{"text":"<p><code>monopolyOdds(8)</code> trebalo bi da vrati niz znakova <code>102400</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(monopolyOdds(8), '102400');"},{"text":"<p><code>monopolyOdds(10)</code> treba da vrati nisku <code>100024</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(monopolyOdds(10), '100024');"},{"text":"<p><code>monopolyOdds(20)</code> treba da vrati niz karaktera <code>100005</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(monopolyOdds(20), '100005');"},{"text":"<p><code>monopolyOdds(4)</code> trebalo bi da vrati niz znakova <code>101524</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(monopolyOdds(4), '101524');"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-1-to-100","dashedName":"problem-84-monopoly-odds","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-85-counting-rectangles","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-83-path-sum-four-ways","id":"5900f3c11000cf542c50fed3","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function arrangedProbability(limit) {\n  // Based on https://www.mathblog.dk/project-euler-100-blue-discs-two-blue/\n  let blue = 15;\n  let discs = 21;\n\n  while (discs < limit) {\n    const nextBlue = 3 * blue + 2 * discs - 2;\n    const nextDiscs = 4 * blue + 3 * discs - 3;\n\n    blue = nextBlue;\n    discs = nextDiscs;\n  }\n  return blue;\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-84-monopoly-odds"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}